nnoremap <Leader>9 :9b<CR>
nnoremap <Leader>0 :10b<CR>

nnoremap <Leader>sb :sb                "对buffer进行水平分屏
nnoremap <Leader>vs :vertical sb       "对buffer进行垂直分屏

nnoremap <leader>path :cd %:p:h         "显示当前路径

